,{"pid":"bb8c116a4c6ce6016bafb3a8b97f326d705edd67","tid":1599471,"uid":189253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"樓主 我都開左呢個戶口 想問下你transfer錢過去既時候收左幾多手續費 因為我見佢要經過一間third party bank先transfer到過去 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：諗住用hsbc transfer"},{"pid":"d15844192f0a3a65877d1eaaf4cc8be62e4780cd","tid":1599471,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民撳爆總行 atm 換美金保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行call loan 然後支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"17d035b0f801adfa2a0f8815bd78eb40f5dcafa5","tid":1599471,"uid":52261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"填緊申請入地址個Flat No. 只可以填數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問Flat 係ABCD嘅巴絲點搞"},{"pid":"75d27d07f52a8abdaa289ee792cc7865aecbcca0","tid":1599471,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"上禮拜申請開戶，video 裡只要求自拍、講出名字同出生日期，同埋拍 bno 護照，兩日後正式開通戶口。之後用 transferwise 匯款，扣除transferwise 扣起的手續費後再扣起14蚊左右usd，款項由離開自己戶口計起，兩日入戶。不過因為 transferwise 匯款平（80幾港元），所以整體依然比銀行匯款平。<br />\n<br />\n因為呢個戶口可買嘅投資產品唔多（只有CFD, 冇margin, 而且收存倉費），定期都冇，仲有我懷疑就算一般usd存款都冇利息（有錯請指正！），所以個人認為只適合小額走資。<br />\n<br />\n我主要都會用CS, TD... 走資兼買吓債券收息，呢個Dukascopy 戶口主要只係貪個歐洲戶口號碼。暫時都唔會申請佢張提款卡。<br />\n<br />\n多謝樓主分享！"},{"pid":"f7bab879472f8ecdc3abefd2690e6a39e891dc73","tid":1599471,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f1d2c2d7541ee9a78148bd6454acf39b3d58e6","tid":1599471,"uid":22506,